## 10. Risks and Mitigations

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-------------|--------|------------|
| Prisma schema mismatch with Phase 1 requirements | Medium | High | Use system user, hide extra fields |
| Validation edge cases | Medium | Medium | Comprehensive integration tests |
| Status enum case sensitivity | High | Low | Explicit transformation functions |
| Empty body validation | Medium | Medium | Custom validator for update |
| XSS in escaped content | Low | High | Use escape() on all text inputs |
| Database connection in tests | Medium | Medium | Proper setup/teardown, connection pooling |

